headline: Is There Now Opportunity in DR Horton After 14% Slide Despite Steady Earnings Growth?
summary: If you’re wondering what to do with D.R. Horton stock these days, you’re definitely not alone. After years of steady growth, the past month has been a bit of a rollercoaster for the share price, down 14.2% over the last 30 days and 11% just this past week. Year-to-date, though, D.R. Horton is still clinging to a 10.9% gain. This suggests some underlying resilience of the business, even when markets get jittery about housing or rates. Of course, it is worth noting that the stock is off 17.5%...
